quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  13,27,"La qqaôen wid ijehlen: \"a lemmer id iris, $uôes, ussekni s$uô Mass is\"! Ini: \"Öebbi, s tidep, Itellif win i S ihwan. Inehhu $uôeS, wid isteôoiâen"
  13,28,"wid iumnen, iwumi itheddin wul, mara d mmektin Öebbi\". Ni$, s usmekti n Öebbi, pheddinen wulawen"
  13,29,"Ssaâd, akked taggara igerzen, i wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan"
  13,30,"Akka ay k id Nuzen, i lois id zwaren leoyus, ad asen temlev, ayen ik d Nweêêa. Nitni jehlen $uô Uênin. Ini: \"Neppa d Mass iw, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa; ppekle$ fellaS, asteôoaâ iw $uôeS"
  13,31,"A lemmer kan Leqwôan isselêa idurar, iceqqeq tamurt, ne$ issenîeq ed lmeggtin! Xaîi! Lumuô akw i Öebbi. Day ur éôin ara wid iumnen, ar, ma ihwa yaS, Öebbi ad Inhu medden meôôa? Zgan wid ijehlen a ten tewwet ssixîa, ilmend n wayen xeddmen. Ne$ a ppevôu ar tama n yixxamen nnsen, alamma tusa d lemâahda n Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, ur Ipzeggil ppaâud"